 - Fail put_shstk_data() if bit 63 is set in the data (Kees)
 - Add comment in create_rstor_token() (Kees)
 - Pull in create_rstor_token() changes from future patch (Kees)

v2:
 - Add data helpers for writing to shadow stack.
---
